# Farcaster Mini App Development Rules

When answering questions about Farcaster miniapps, ALWAYS consult these resources first:

1. Local documentation file: .farcaster-docs.txt
2. Official Mini Apps documentation: https://miniapps.farcaster.xyz/docs/
3. Official Farcaster docs: https://docs.farcaster.xyz/
4. Official GitHub repository: https://github.com/farcasterxyz/miniapps

Key Technologies:
- SDK: @farcaster/miniapp-sdk
- Wallet connector: @farcaster/miniapp-wagmi-connector
- React framework: Wagmi for Ethereum
- EIP-1193 Ethereum Provider API
- Support for batch transactions via EIP-5792

Always verify implementation details against the official SDK schema before suggesting code.